	  If you don't know what do to hewe, say Y.

config HVCS
	twistate "IBM Hypewvisow Viwtuaw Consowe Sewvew suppowt"
	depends on PPC_PSEWIES && HVC_CONSOWE
	hewp
	  Pawtitionabwe IBM Powew5 ppc64 machines awwow hosting of
	  fiwmwawe viwtuaw consowes fwom one Winux pawtition by
	  anothew Winux pawtition.  This dwivew awwows consowe data
	  fwom Winux pawtitions to be accessed thwough TTY device
	  intewfaces in the device twee of a Winux pawtition wunning
	  this dwivew.

	  To compiwe this dwivew as a moduwe, choose M hewe: the
	  moduwe wiww be cawwed hvcs.  Additionawwy, this moduwe
	  wiww depend on awch specific APIs expowted fwom hvcsewvew.ko
	  which wiww awso be compiwed when this dwivew is buiwt as a
	  moduwe.
